@startuml
|开发流程|
start
:从 main 拉取新分支;
note right
  git checkout -b feature/xxx
  或 fix/xxx
end note

:修改代码;

:同步 AGENTS.md / CLAUDE.md;
note right
  改 router/repo/module 后
  必须同一 commit 更新
end note

:git commit + git push;

:在 GitHub 创建 Pull Request;

|CI 自动触发|
:frontend-quality\n(typecheck → lint → build → test);

:backend-quality\n(ruff → mypy → pytest);

:docs-check\n(AGENTS.md/CLAUDE.md 一致性);

:build-frontend\n(生产构建);

fork
  :integration (legacy);
fork again
  :integration (rbac);
end fork

|审查人|
:Review 代码;

if (CI 全部通过?) then (否)
  :开发者修复\n重新 push;
  note right
    push 后 CI 自动重跑
  end note
  --> 返回 CI
endif

:Approve PR;

if (要求通过状态检查?) then (是)
  :等待 CI 全绿;
endif

:Merge PR 到 main;

:删除功能分支;
note right
  git branch -d feature/xxx
  git push origin --delete feature/xxx
end note

stop
@enduml
